---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service · NorCal EVs"
  description="The basics of using the NorCal EVs website and community."
>
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="kicker">Legal</span>
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:36px">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="doc">
        <p class="doc-updated">Placeholder terms. Final language is being prepared and will replace this draft before launch.</p>

        <h2>Using this site</h2>
        <p>This website is provided by NorCal EVs for the cross-brand EV community in Northern California. By using it, you agree to use it lawfully and respectfully, and not to disrupt the site or other members.</p>

        <h2>Community membership</h2>
        <p>Membership tiers, benefits, and pricing are described on the <a href="/membership">Membership</a> page and may change as the community grows. Joining and participating in events is subject to our community guidelines, which are shared in our online hub.</p>

        <h2>Events</h2>
        <p>Event details, locations, and timing can change. Attend at your own discretion and follow any guidance provided by event organizers and venues.</p>

        <h2>Content and trademarks</h2>
        <p>Vehicle brand names and logos referenced on this site belong to their respective owners and are used only to describe the cross-brand nature of the community. NorCal EVs is not affiliated with or endorsed by any vehicle manufacturer.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:contact@norcalevs.org">contact@norcalevs.org</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
